{"tid":1969084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Joe BIden : 「中國」防疫數據不可信, 要求「中國」容許美國科學家調查病毒起因","createTime":"2020-04-12T07:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T06:33:04.000Z","uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"446975daaed345d9803645c1ddde2752bd4fc5a7","tid":1969084,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"原來佢係今年2月26日已經咁講.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; (果陣時, 美國疫情仲未大爆發)<br />\n<br />\nJoe BIden : 我不會相信「中國」防疫數據, 如果我是總統, 我會堅持要求「中國」容許美國科學家徹底調查病毒起因. &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/2002/26/se.02.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftranscripts.cnn.com%2FTRANSCRIPTS%2F2002%2F26%2Fse.02.html&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=c65da535\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftranscripts.cnn.com%2FTRANSCRIPTS%2F2002%2F26%2Fse.02.html&h=0eaaffeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/2002/26/se.02.html</a><br />\n<br />\nCNN LIVE EVENT/SPECIAL<br />\nTown Hall with Democratic Presidential Candidate, Former Vice President Joe Biden. Aired 8-9p ET<br />\n<strong>Aired February 26, 2020 - 20:00   ET</strong><br />\n<br />\nQUESTION: My question is, COVID-19 is a serious threat to our health and the economy. If you were president, what would you be doing?<br />\n<br />\nBIDEN: &nbsp;.... The last point I'd make, and I know I'm going to get a lot of questions, is that what we did -- what I would do were I president now, <strong>I would not be taking China's word for it. I would insist that China allow our scientists in to make a hard determination of how it started, where it's from, how far along it is. Because that is not happening now.</strong>"},{"pid":"80ee452b57a1742656250ad920fad14bf16d7f42","tid":1969084,"uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"但我暫時仲係傾向Trump連任 (因為有Mike Pence<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"a70de0ac7b690437fe35438e4404a64a9d10471a","tid":1969084,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa9f4b8b7e3954a42d234f10110fb83cca7f4ed","tid":1969084,"uid":45613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:47:53.000Z","msg":"終國<del>防疫數據</del>不可信"},{"pid":"351923652cf445e8b25531eab064a90652f7e7cd","tid":1969084,"uid":237465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"這個是常識吧 !<br />\n<br />\nthis is common sense only."},{"pid":"fc111a274893e115ed5a9d36f5e2c1e41decb77f","tid":1969084,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:48:54.000Z","msg":"美國民意冇可能逆轉"},{"pid":"47e15439de0c412fabdfd15278d7d57ac43f357c","tid":1969084,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"但點樣可以要求比美科學家入去查?"},{"pid":"edde0f3c0b0c2ee38a512a174c77eb236fe3eb5c","tid":1969084,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"351923652cf445e8b25531eab064a90652f7e7cd","tid":1969084,"uid":237465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"這個是常識吧 !<br />\n<br />\nthis is common sense only."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"果時(國際上)未有太多人公開質疑中國防疫數據.<br />\n<br />\n當時,美國國務院都有表示質疑, 但Trump仲稱讚緊習近平防疫...."},{"pid":"7907f7ce8a7d2ed3d14c2cc8c79bf11434beaa7d","tid":1969084,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc111a274893e115ed5a9d36f5e2c1e41decb77f","tid":1969084,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:48:54.000Z","msg":"美國民意冇可能逆轉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"你意思係咩民意先<img src=\"/assets/